      "fullText" : "Step 1.) Start with the Work\n\nWhen you cold email someone––they'll immediately think:\n\n\"Is this person worth my time?\"\n\nProve it with your work.\n\nWhether it's a:\n\n• Portfolio site\n• A pdf\n• Your Twitter account\n\nExpensive sites are overrated, just make it easy to view work.",
